#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn46.19"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.19:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.19:0.2"
msgid "2. Gilānavagga "
msgstr "2. Sick "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn46.19:0.3"
msgid "19. Ariyasutta "
msgstr "19. Noble "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn46.19:1.1"
msgid "“Sattime, bhikkhave, bojjhaṅgā bhāvitā bahulīkatā ariyā niyyānikā nīyanti takkarassa sammā dukkhakkhayāya. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when these seven awakening factors are developed and cultivated they are noble and emancipating, and bring one who practices them to the complete ending of suffering. "

msgctxt "sn46.19:1.2"
msgid "Katame satta? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "sn46.19:1.3"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgo … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo—"
msgstr "The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity. "

msgctxt "sn46.19:1.4"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, satta bojjhaṅgā bhāvitā bahulīkatā ariyā niyyānikā nīyanti takkarassa sammā dukkhakkhayāyā”ti. "
msgstr "When these seven awakening factors are developed and cultivated they are noble and emancipating, and bring one who practices them to the complete ending of suffering.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.19:1.5"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

